               <p>I lost a pig; it was purchased by Hamilton of the prisoner. I claimed the pig, and it was returned to my possession.</p>

               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I found the pig in Holborn. I did not know who it belonged to. I kept it a month; I had no victuals to give it so I sold it.</p>
